This paper discusses the techniques for automatic text summarization, which involves natural language processing and information retrieval. Therefore, it is most likely to belong to the sub-category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). However, it also involves machine learning and data mining techniques, which are covered in sub-categories such as Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS).
